refentry:
elements street street Element
street &street.purpose;
&street.synopsis.gen; Description
In postal addresses, the Street element contains the street address portion of the Address. If an address contains more than one line of street address information, each line should appear in its own Street.
Processing expectations
&format.inline; In an Address, this element may inherit the verbatim qualities of an address.
&street.parents.gen; &street.children.gen;
See Also &street.seealso.gen;
Examples
For examples, see &street.example.seealso.gen;.
